Header include order:
 - Alphabetize within subgroups, newlines between groups
 - Group 1
   - linux/*
   - sys/types.h
   - sys/*
   - networking
 - Group 2
   - headers directly in /usr/include (e.g. string.h, unistd.h, stdint.h)
 - Group 3
   - Standard C++ headers
   - Boost headers
 - Group 4
   - external libraries (e.g. OpenSSL), grouped by library
